library(dplyr)

reporter.aves <- aves.dta %>% 
  group_by(reporteriso3) %>% 
  summarise(ave_weighted= weighted.mean(NNeg.BP1, tradevalue, na.rm = TRUE))

reporter.aves$names <- c("Australia", "Brunei", "China", "Hong Kong", "India", "Indonesia", "Japan", "Kazakhstan",
   "Cambodia", "Korea, Rep.", "Lao", "Malaysia", "Nepal", "New Zealand", "Pakistan",
   "Phillipines", "Russia", "Singapore", "Thailand", "Turkey", "Vietnam")
reporter.aves$grp <- c(3, 3, 2, 3, 2, 2, 3, 2, 1, 3, 1, 2, 1, 3, 1, 2, 2, 3, 2, 3, 1)

reporter.aves<-reporter.aves[!(reporter.aves$ave_weighted=="NaN"),]

library(ggplot2)

ggplot(data = reporter.aves, aes(x = grp, y = ave_weighted, fill = reporteriso3)) +
    geom_bar(stat="identity", position ="dodge") +
    geom_text(aes(label= reporteriso3), vjust= 1.3, size=3.5) +
    theme_minimal()
